originalText.text: I have been so happy with Doc. Selick! I tried three different fertility specialists and offices before I found her and she was the nicest and most professional, as well as every single staff member in her office. She got me pregnant with my son who I gave birth to a year ago and I am now working with her on my second. She was very patient with me and took her time explaining the process, her offices are the warmest and most cheerful of all the ones I've been in and made me feel better than any of the others. I don't know why there are such bad reviews about her and I'm glad I didn't see them before or I would have missed out on a great doctor. She was trying everything to avoid surgery with me until it was the last resort, and she did everything so we don't waste my precious embryos. I can go on and on about how great she is... Most sincerely!

originalText.text: I would highly recommend Dr. Amy Bloomgarden and Dr. Caryn Selick.  They are both responsive, patient, caring and extremely knowledgeable.  Their office staff is very helpful and pleasant and they are always willing to do whatever it takes to accomplish what the patient needs.
